    <string name="mcp_skill_claw_prompt">Connect to the current KeiOS MCP service, then call keios.mcp.claw.skill.guide(mode=auto). Register the SKILL.md content from the response as a Claw Skill named “KeiOS MCP Skill”; after that, run keios.health.ping and keios.mcp.runtime.status to verify connectivity. For scheduled tasks or composed skills, read keios://skill/workflows.md and use keios.mcp.workflow.plan or keios.mcp.workflow.blueprints.</string>
